verbose_text: However, the ZP must indirectly lower the dissociation of BMP9 from OR, because, as previously observed by surface plasmon resonance (SPR) using an OR construct truncated at P338, the dissociation rate constant (k off) of the OR - BMP9 complex is significantly higher than that of ECTO-BMP9 (XREF_TABLE).
evidence: ZP must indirectly lower the dissociation of BMP9
